</html>
A couple of quiet fixes I made from the source: I moved the 1985, 1987, and 1988 rows into proper chronological order, and I normalized circa 1988 for Let Them Eat Art to 1988 in the year column since the row already gives a specific date of October 26, 1988. 
1980s-group-exhibitions


Send the next group decade page and I’ll keep the exact same structure.


Sources


1990s-group-exhibitions.md
File

I have the 1990s group page source. There are a couple of path inconsistencies and several rows out of order, so I’m standardizing it to the same exhibition-list template and cleaning the chronology as I go.

Thought for 5s
Here is the cleaned, matching version for the 1990s group exhibitions page. I kept your entries, detail-page links, and image references, but removed the old markdown-table/glow setup and put everything into the same catalogue template as the other decade pages. I also reordered the rows chronologically and fixed one image path inconsistency from the source. 
1990s-group-exhibitions


The main path fix: the Urban Jungle row was using ../images/... while the rest of the page uses ../../images/.... I normalized that so it will behave like the other rows on GitHub Pages. 
1990s-group-exhibitions


Use this as ron-english-catalogue-raisonne/exhibitions/group/1990s-group-exhibitions.html:

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>1990s Group Exhibitions | Ron English Catalogue Raisonné</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/styles.css" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --border:#e5e7eb;
      --muted:#4b5563;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      --radius:18px;
      --bg:#ffffff;
      --panel:#f8fafc;
    }

    *{
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:#111;
      background:var(--bg);
    }

    .wrap{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:28px 18px 60px;
    }

    .nav-pills{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .nav-pill{
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid #d6e1ff;
      background:#fff;
      color:#111;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .nav-pill:hover{
      background:#f3f6ff;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);
      margin:0 0 10px;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
    }

    .subtitle{
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:72ch;
      margin:0;
    }

    .intro{
      margin-top:24px;
      padding:18px 20px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:var(--panel);
    }

    .intro p{
      margin:0;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.65;
      color:#1f2937;
      max-width:75ch;
    }

    .listing-wrap{
      margin-top:28px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .listing-header{
      padding:18px 20px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .listing-header h2{
      margin:0 0 6px;
      font-size:22px;
    }

    .listing-header p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .table-scroll{
      overflow-x:auto;
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      font-size:16px;
    }

    th,
    td{
      padding:14px 14px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      text-align:left;
      vertical-align:middle;
    }

    th{
      font-size:13px;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#6b7280;
      background:#f9fafb;
    }

    td{
      font-size:15px;
      color:#111;
    }

    tr:last-child td{
      border-bottom:none;
    }

    .thumb-link{
      display:inline-block;
      line-height:0;
    }

    .mural-thumb{
      width:64px;
      height:64px;
      object-fit:cover;
      border-radius:10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      display:block;
      background:#f3f4f6;
    }

    .title-link{
      color:#111;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:600;
    }

    .title-link:hover{
      text-decoration:underline;
    }

    .venue{
      color:#1f2937;
    }

    .notes{
      margin-top:28px;
      padding-top:18px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.65;
    }

    footer{
      margin-top:30px;
      padding-top:16px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    @media (max-width:720px){
      table{
        font-size:14px;
      }

      th,
      td{
        padding:12px 10px;
      }

      .mural-thumb{
        width:56px;
        height:56px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

