2005-2009-group-exhibitions.md
File

I’ve got the 2005–2009 source. It has the same old table styling as the others, plus several 2005 and 2009 rows out of sequence, so I’m standardizing the template and cleaning the chronology.

Thought for 4 seconds
Here is the cleaned, matching version for the 2005–2009 group exhibitions page. I kept your entries, detail-page links, and image references, but removed the old markdown-table/glow setup and put everything into the same catalogue template as the other decade pages. I also reordered the rows so 2005 and 2009 read in clean chronological sequence. 
2005-2009-group-exhibitions


Use this as ron-english-catalogue-raisonne/exhibitions/group/2005-2009-group-exhibitions.html:

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>2005–2009 Group Exhibitions | Ron English Catalogue Raisonné</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/styles.css" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --border:#e5e7eb;
      --muted:#4b5563;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      --radius:18px;
      --bg:#ffffff;
      --panel:#f8fafc;
    }

    *{
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:#111;
      background:var(--bg);
    }

    .wrap{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:28px 18px 60px;
    }

    .nav-pills{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .nav-pill{
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid #d6e1ff;
      background:#fff;
      color:#111;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .nav-pill:hover{
      background:#f3f6ff;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);
      margin:0 0 10px;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
    }

    .subtitle{
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:72ch;
      margin:0;
    }

    .intro{
      margin-top:24px;
      padding:18px 20px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:var(--panel);
    }

    .intro p{
      margin:0;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.65;
      color:#1f2937;
      max-width:75ch;
    }

    .listing-wrap{
      margin-top:28px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .listing-header{
      padding:18px 20px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .listing-header h2{
      margin:0 0 6px;
      font-size:22px;
    }

    .listing-header p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .table-scroll{
      overflow-x:auto;
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      font-size:16px;
    }

    th,
    td{
      padding:14px 14px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      text-align:left;
      vertical-align:middle;
    }

    th{
      font-size:13px;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#6b7280;
      background:#f9fafb;
    }

    td{
      font-size:15px;
      color:#111;
    }

    tr:last-child td{
      border-bottom:none;
    }

    .thumb-link{
      display:inline-block;
      line-height:0;
    }

    .mural-thumb{
      width:64px;
      height:64px;
      object-fit:cover;
      border-radius:10px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      display:block;
      background:#f3f4f6;
    }

    .title-link{
      color:#111;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:600;
    }

    .title-link:hover{
      text-decoration:underline;
    }

    .venue{
      color:#1f2937;
    }

    .notes{
      margin-top:28px;
      padding-top:18px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.65;
    }

    footer{
      margin-top:30px;
      padding-top:16px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    @media (max-width:720px){
      table{
        font-size:14px;
      }

      th,
      td{
        padding:12px 10px;
      }

      .mural-thumb{
        width:56px;
        height:56px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

