Thought for 5s
This is a good start. The content is there, but I would rework it into the same site structure and visual language as the decade pages, so every exhibition detail page feels like part of one system. The uploaded file currently uses markdown-style headings and an inline image path that goes up three levels, which is more fragile than it needs to be from this folder. 
annus-mirabilis-kwikwash-galler…


Since this page will live here:

ron-english-catalogue-raisonne/exhibitions/solo/1970s-1980s-solo-shows/annus-mirabilis-kwikwash-gallery-1980.html
the image path should be:

../../images/Exhibitions/Solo/annus-mirabilis-kwikwash-gallery-1979-1.jpg
not ../../../..., because the file is only two levels below the catalogue root images folder.

I would also rename the file to match the year shown on the main table. Right now your listing page uses 1980 for this row, even though the uploaded draft says c. 1979 (December 7). So the filename should stay consistent with whatever date you decide to display publicly.

Here is a cleaned HTML version for the individual page:

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Annus ... Mirabilis | Ron English Catalogue Raisonné</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/styles.css" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --border:#e5e7eb;
      --muted:#4b5563;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      --radius:18px;
      --bg:#ffffff;
      --panel:#f8fafc;
    }

    *{
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:#111;
      background:var(--bg);
    }

    .wrap{
      max-width:1000px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:28px 18px 60px;
    }

    .nav-pills{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .nav-pill{
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid #d6e1ff;
      background:#fff;
      color:#111;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .nav-pill:hover{
      background:#f3f6ff;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,54px);
      margin:0 0 10px;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
    }

    .subtitle{
      font-size:18px;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:70ch;
      margin:0;
    }

    .hero{
      margin-top:24px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .hero img{
      width:100%;
      max-height:620px;
      object-fit:contain;
      display:block;
      background:#f3f4f6;
    }

    .caption{
      padding:12px 16px 16px;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.5;
      color:var(--muted);
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .meta-card,
    .text-card,
    .sources-card{
      margin-top:24px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      background:#fff;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .card-head{
      padding:16px 18px;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .card-head h2{
      margin:0;
      font-size:22px;
    }

    .card-body{
      padding:18px;
    }

    .meta-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:180px 1fr;
      gap:12px 18px;
    }

    .meta-label{
      font-size:13px;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#6b7280;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .meta-value{
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.6;
      color:#111;
    }

    .card-body p{
      margin:0 0 14px;
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.7;
      color:#1f2937;
    }

    .card-body p:last-child{
      margin-bottom:0;
    }

    .sources-card ul{
      margin:0;
      padding-left:20px;
    }

    .sources-card li{
      font-size:16px;
      line-height:1.7;
      color:#1f2937;
    }

    footer{
      margin-top:30px;
      padding-top:16px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    @media (max-width:700px){
      .meta-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
        gap:6px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <nav class="nav-pills" aria-label="Site navigation">
