<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <nav class="nav-pills" aria-label="Site navigation">
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../../index.html">Catalogue home</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Solo exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../1970s-1980s-solo-exhibitions.html">1970s & 1980s</a>
    </nav>

    <header>
      <h1><em>Beyond the Groovy Planet — New Stuff by Ron English</em></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Levlowe Gallery, New York, 1980.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" aria-label="Exhibition image">
      <img src="../../images/Exhibitions/Solo/Beyond-the-Groovy-Planet.jpg" alt="Ron English — Beyond the Groovy Planet, Levlowe Gallery, 1980">
      <div class="caption">
        Exhibition postcard for <em>Beyond the Groovy Planet — New Stuff by Ron English</em>, Levlowe Gallery, New York.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meta-card" aria-label="Exhibition details">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Exhibition Details</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-label">Year</div>
          <div class="meta-value">1980</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Title</div>
          <div class="meta-value"><em>Beyond the Groovy Planet — New Stuff by Ron English</em></div>

          <div class="meta-label">Venue</div>
          <div class="meta-value">Levlowe Gallery</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Location</div>
          <div class="meta-value">200 East Third Street, New York, NY, USA</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Date</div>
          <div class="meta-value">Friday, November 28, 1980</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Time</div>
          <div class="meta-value">7–10 p.m.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-card" aria-label="Notes">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Notes</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          <em>Beyond the Groovy Planet</em> is one of Ron English’s earliest documented solo exhibitions in New York. Held at Levlowe Gallery in 1980, the show was presented as “new stuff” by English.
        </p>
        <p>
          The illustrated showcard suggests an early visual language built from surreal distortion, cartoon logic, and psychedelic imagery. Multi-headed figures, floating eyes, and exaggerated forms point toward themes that would later reappear in his more widely known Popaganda work.
        </p>
        <p>
          The exhibition took place in the East Village on Friday, November 28, from 7 to 10 p.m., and the hand-drawn postcard reflects the underground downtown energy surrounding English’s early New York activity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sources-card" aria-label="Sources">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Sources</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Printed exhibition postcard for <em>Beyond the Groovy Planet — New Stuff by Ron English</em>, Levlowe Gallery, New York, November 28, 1980.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <a href="../1970s-1980s-solo-exhibitions.html#levlowe-gallery-beyond-the-groovy-planet-1980-row">Back to 1970s–1980s solo exhibitions</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

