<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <nav class="nav-pills" aria-label="Site navigation">
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../../index.html">Catalogue home</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Solo exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../1970s-1980s-solo-exhibitions.html">1970s & 1980s</a>
    </nav>

    <header>
      <h1><em>Photographs by Ron English</em></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Midtown Y Photography Gallery, New York, 1988.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" aria-label="Exhibition image">
      <img src="../../images/Exhibitions/Solo/Midtown-Y-Photo copy.jpg" alt="Ron English — Photographs Exhibition at Midtown Y Photography Gallery, 1988">
      <div class="caption">
        Showcard for <em>Photographs by Ron English</em>, Midtown Y Photography Gallery, New York, 1988.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meta-card" aria-label="Exhibition details">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Exhibition Details</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-label">Year</div>
          <div class="meta-value">1988</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Title</div>
          <div class="meta-value"><em>Photographs by Ron English</em></div>

          <div class="meta-label">Venue</div>
          <div class="meta-value">Midtown Y Photography Gallery</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Location</div>
          <div class="meta-value">344 East 14th Street, New York, NY, USA</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Dates</div>
          <div class="meta-value">May 19 – June 26, 1988</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Opening reception</div>
          <div class="meta-value">Thursday, May 19, 1988, 5–8 p.m.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-card" aria-label="Notes">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Notes</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          In 1988, Midtown Y Photography Gallery presented <em>Photographs by Ron English</em> in New York. The documented dates run from May 19 through June 26, with an opening reception on the first evening of the exhibition.
        </p>
        <p>
          This exhibition helps document a photographic phase in Ron English’s early career, before his later Popaganda work became more widely recognized. The surviving records place the show within a setting associated with emerging and experimental photography.
        </p>
        <p>
          The exhibition is important for tracing English’s activity in New York during the late 1980s and for showing that photography formed a visible part of his public exhibition history during this period.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sources-card" aria-label="Sources">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Sources</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Showcard for <em>Photographs by Ron English</em>, Midtown Y Photography Gallery, May 19 – June 26, 1988.</li>
          <li>Midtown Y Photography Gallery Records, 1972–1996.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

