<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <nav class="nav-pills" aria-label="Site navigation">
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../../index.html">Catalogue home</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../index.html">Solo exhibitions</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="../1970s-1980s-solo-exhibitions.html">1970s & 1980s</a>
    </nav>

    <header>
      <h1><em>Ron English</em></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        OK Harris Works of Art, New York, 1989.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="hero-grid" aria-label="Exhibition images">
      <div class="hero">
        <img src="../../images/Exhibitions/Solo/trompe-l'oeil-ok-harris-1989-1.jpg" alt="Ron English solo exhibition at OK Harris Works of Art, 1989">
        <div class="caption">
          Exhibition card for <em>Ron English</em>, OK Harris Works of Art, New York, 1989.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero">
        <img src="../../images/Exhibitions/Solo/OK-Harris-1.jpg" alt="Ron English solo exhibition material for OK Harris Works of Art, 1989">
        <div class="caption">
          Additional exhibition material for <em>Ron English</em>, OK Harris Works of Art, 1989.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meta-card" aria-label="Exhibition details">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Exhibition Details</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-label">Year</div>
          <div class="meta-value">1989</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Title</div>
          <div class="meta-value"><em>Ron English</em></div>

          <div class="meta-label">Venue</div>
          <div class="meta-value">OK Harris Works of Art</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Location</div>
          <div class="meta-value">New York, New York, USA</div>

          <div class="meta-label">Dates</div>
          <div class="meta-value">March 4–25, 1989</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-card" aria-label="Notes">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Notes</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          This solo exhibition at Ivan Karp’s OK Harris Works of Art presented Ron English’s early photographic pieces and illusionistic staged scenes. The show extended his investigation into constructed reality through tableaux built in the studio and photographed as direct images rather than darkroom manipulations.
        </p>
        <p>
          The exhibition placed these works in dialogue with the gallery’s reputation for conceptual and photo-based work. It also helps document an early moment when English’s interest in illusion, staged perception, and media language entered a more formal gallery context in New York.
        </p>
        <p>
          As one of his first documented New York solo exhibitions, the show marks an important step in the development of ideas that would later surface in billboard interventions, POPaganda imagery, and large-scale painting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sources-card" aria-label="Sources">
      <div class="card-head">
        <h2>Sources</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://gallery98.org/2021/ok-harris-gallery-ron-english-card-1989">Gallery 98 – <em>Ron English, OK Harris Gallery</em> (exhibition card, 1989)</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.okharris.com/previous/2ExhSchedSept1979-July1989.pdf">OK Harris – <em>Exhibition Schedule 1979–1989</em> (PDF)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <a href="../1970s-1980s-solo-exhibitions.html#ok-harris-ron-english-1989-row">Back to 1970s–1980s solo exhibitions</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
